#. type: Plain text
#: docs/books/admin_guide/06-users.md:26
msgid ""
"Each user is a member of at least one group: **this is their main group**."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/books/admin_guide/06-users.md:28
msgid "Several users can be part of the same group."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/books/admin_guide/06-users.md:30
msgid ""
"Users can belong to other groups. These users are *invited* to these "
"**secondary groups**."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/books/admin_guide/06-users.md:33
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"!!! Note\n"
"    Each user has a primary group and can be invited into one or more secondary groups.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/books/admin_guide/06-users.md:35
msgid ""
"Groups and users are managed by their unique numerical identifiers `GID` and "
"`UID`."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/books/admin_guide/06-users.md:39
